title: Robert Mueller Submits Russia Report
itunes:title: Robert Mueller Submits Russia Report
description:
Special counsel Robert Mueller has turned over his long-awaited final report on the contentious Russia investigation. For analysis, Kevin spoke with Andy Surabian, Republican Strategist and former Special Assistant to President Trump and Deputy WH Strategist, and Gene Rossi, Former Federal Prosecutor.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
